    • readCsv

      public static void readCsv(String fileName) throws FileNotFoundException, ParseException
      This method read each line of file. Save in a String line. Split each data in an array. Then assigns the data to the appropriate data type. Sends each data to the Constructor to create a new object, finally, adding to ArrayList.
      Throws:
      FileNotFound - if the file doesnt exists and Parse Conversion is the conversion has a problem.
